operators.name: Distinct
operators.description: Suppress duplicate items emitted by an Observable

operators.name: Filter
operators.description: Emit only those items from an Observable that pass a predicate test

operators.name: IgnoreElements
operators.description: Do not emit any items from an Observable but mirror its termination notification

operators.name: SkipLast
operators.description: Suppress the last n items emitted by an Observable

operators.name: Skip
operators.description: Suppress the first n items emitted by an Observable

operators.name: TakeLast
operators.description: Emit only the last n items emitted by an Observable

operators.name: Take
operators.description: Emit only the first n items emitted by an Observable
